The paper focuses on the evaluation of different deep architectures for image recognition and object detection, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). It also explores the properties and implementation details of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN), which is a popular machine learning technique (cs.LG). The paper discusses the comparison of different methods and the identification of useful properties, which are common themes in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper provides source code and models, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
